is seeking bids for water-network expansion and upgrades in the
northeastern towns of Flamanzi and Frumusica under a contract
estimated at 85.5 million lei ($25 million).  The utility is waiting for bids until Aug. 12, according to
a June 8  procurement notice  published on the European Unionâ€™s
